com.serena.dmclient.objects
Class TypeOptions

java.lang.Object
  com.serena.dmclient.objects.TypeOptions

public class TypeOptions
extends java.lang.Object

Encapsulates all predefined Dimensions object type options that might be enabled to a specific Dimensions object type.

ITEM_DONT_RESTRICT_UPDATE_AT_INITIAL_STATE

public static final int ITEM_DONT_RESTRICT_UPDATE_AT_INITIAL_STATE
If updating at the initial lifecycle state is allowed, do not restrict the update only to the item creator. Note that this flag is the reverse of the equivalent checkbox in the Administration Console. For instance, if you wish to restrict item updates at initial states in Administration Console then the checkbox should be selected but here the option should be cleared in the bit-flag passed to Type.setOptions(int).

See Also:
